snippet.title: Orbital Strike VR - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1350780/Orbital_Strike_VR/

Website: https://orbitalstrikevr.com/

Experience thrilling fleet battles through zero-g orbital combat with support for drop-in co-op multiplayer. Make good tactical decisions to build and direct fire support assets and take back humanity's skies from a relentless enemy.
